NAME
    find - search for files in a directory hierarchy

SYNOPSIS
    find [path...] [expression] 
    expression = options + tests + actions

TESTS

    Numeric arguments can be specified as

    +n  for greater than n,
    -n  for less than n,
    n   for exactly n.

    -name pattern
    
    -type type(b, c, d, p, f, l, s, D)
        b   block (buffered) special
        c   character (unbuffered) special
        p   named pipe
        l   symbolic link
        s   socket
        D   door(Solaris)


    -size size(b, c, w, k, M, G)
        b   512 bytes
        c   one byte
        w   two bytes

    -atime n
    -anewer file
    -atime n

    -cmin n
    -cnewer file
    -ctime n

    -mmin n
    -mtime n
    -newer file

    -perm mode
    -user username
    -group groupname

ACTIONS

    -delete

    -ls

    -exec command ;
        ';' need to be escape to '/;'

        

